    "body": "<!--\r\nPlease, be as descriptive as possible.  Issues lacking detail, or for any other reason than to report a bug, may be closed without action.\r\n-->\r\n\r\n### Expected\r\nWhen dark mode is enabled, rotating to landscape orientation while editing should retain dark mode.\r\n\r\n### Observed\r\nInstead, the editor switches to light mode.\r\n\r\n### Reproduced\r\n1. Enable dark mode in Simplenote's app settings.\r\n2. Open a note and start editing.\r\n3. Rotate to landscape orientation.\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/42454301/124658653-05cea980-de72-11eb-8f8b-0a9fec888ba7.mp4\r\n\r\nDevice Make: Google\r\nDevice Model: Pixel 3\r\nAndroid Version: 11\r\nSimplenote Version: 2.18\r\n\r\n",
